@using V308CMS.Common
@using V308CMS.Data
@using V308CMS.Helpers
@model V308CMS.Data.NewsIndexPageContainer
@{  
    Layout = "~/Views/themes/" + ViewBag.domain + "/Layout/Layout.cshtml";
  
}
@section header {
    <title>Video</title>
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="Mpstart, Tin tức">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Tin tức, thương mại điện tử, điện thoại">
}
@section Breadcrumb{
    <div class="clearfix breadcrumb-wrap">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="breadcrumb">
                    <h2></h2>
                    <a href="/" title="Back to the frontpage">Trang chủ</a>
                    <span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-circle"></i></span>
                    <strong>
                        Video
                    </strong>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
}
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12 col-main">
        <div class="content-blog">                
            @if (Model.ListNews.IsHasData()){
                <ul class="row">
                    @foreach (var video in Model.ListNews)
                    {
                        <li class="col-xs-4">
                             @Html.Action("VideoItemBlock", "Block", new News {ID = video.ID,Title = video.Title,Summary = video.Summary})
                        </li>

                    }
                </ul>
            }

        </div>
    </div>
</div>
